reviews.name: siti fatimah az-zahraa
reviews.text:
⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Gentle, compassionate, and truly dedicated dental care

Dr. Leong gave outstanding treatment to my mother with deep care and professionalism. She explained the procedure clearly, ensured my mother’s comfort, and performed a painless tooth extraction that exceeded our expectations.

What truly touched us was the follow-up from the clinic the next day initiated by Dr. Leong herself to check on my mother’s recovery. They also offered thoughtful aftercare advice, which showed their genuine concern beyond the clinic walls.

The clinic staffs were friendly, warm, and incredibly helpful throughout. It was a reassuring experience from start to finish.

Highly recommended for anyone seeking respectful, gentle, and patient-focused dental care.
reviews.responseFromOwnerText:
Dear Siti fatimah az-zahraa,

Thank you so much for your kind and thoughtful words. We’re truly honored to have had the opportunity to care for your mother and are so glad to hear that her experience was reassuring and comfortable. Dr. Leong and our entire team are deeply committed to providing gentle, compassionate, and patient-centered care, and it means the world to know that this came through in your visit.

Your feedback reminds us why we do what we do. Thank you again for your trust and for recommending us—it’s patients and families like yours who make our work so meaningful. We wish your mother a continued smooth recovery and look forward to caring for you both in the future.

Warmest regards,
Smilebay dental Air Itam

reviews.name: Ace Stefan
reviews.text:
Been using this particular dental for over 4-5 years.

A big shout out to the receptionist make me felt welcoming each time I came here as well as being very informative about how things works at smilebay, a peace of mind.

Dentists are excellent too, keeping the treatment very structural and hygiene throughout. Most importantly, they don’t push you for any ‘additional unnecessary’ treatment. Once I was asking for whitening treatment, the dentist was given clear info with great detail and demonstration without pushing you to take it. Big plus!

Highly recommend anyone!
reviews.responseFromOwnerText:
Dear Ace Stefan ,

Thank you for taking the time to share your valuable feedback with us. We greatly appreciate your kind comments and are thrilled to hear that you had a pleasant experience during your recent visit. It was truly our pleasure to serve you, and we are glad that we met your expectations.

We take great pride in providing exceptional service to all our customers, and your positive feedback serves as a motivation to our team to continue to strive for excellence.

Once again, thank you for choosing us, and we hope to serve you again

Warmest regard,
Smilebay Dental Air Itam

it’s very rarely of me to spend my time and write a google review . but unfortunately something happened and reached my limit today when i went to this clinic . yesterday i had a an extreme fever , with sore throat like something stuck inside my throat and today when i woke up i could barely walk or stand cause i had a strong headache , but i could feel my body temp lowers today . thats why ive decided to go to this clinic.  but then the doctor who diagnosed me , treated me like i am some kind of patient that come for nothing. i dont know if this is the right ethics or what,  he even shouted at me, and he says there’s nothing wrong with me . he said he gave me medicine for fever (paracetamol) and he even said i wont give you the medicine for sore throat ,he said if you want that one you can just get at shop somewhere 😄 im offended on the way i was being treated , i wasn’t given a chance to explain my condition since he shouted at me . i will not support any government clinic again after this .

if this is how its supposed to be , shouldn’t have come to this clinic and dont mind spend some pennies on private clinic .

reviews.responseFromOwnerText:
Dear Miss Shazy Sahrulazizi,

Wow! Reviews like madam had made our day! We’re overjoyed that your daughter had such a positive first experience with us : scaling and cleaning can sometimes feel intimidating, so hearing that it was pain-free and even enjoyable is the best compliment we could receive! 

Our team works hard to create a welcoming, kid-friendly environment, and knowing your little one is already excited for her next visit tells us we’re doing our job right. (The toy egg machine is always a hit—we love seeing those happy post-treatment smiles!) 

Thank you for trusting us with her dental care and for spreading the word. We can't wait to see you both at the next appointment!

reviews.name: KOOI NGAN CHIN
reviews.text:
最近在这家牙科进行了implant over denture(植体式假牙），整个过程非常满意。首先，诊所的环境非常整洁、舒适，让人感到放松。接待人员热情有礼，服务周到，每一步都详细说明，让人感到非常安心。

Dr Lim Sze Ming 非常专业、耐心，在治疗前详细检查了我的牙齿状况，并为我制定了合适的治疗方案。在整个治疗过程中，医生细心操作，尽量减轻我的不适感，还不断询问我的感受，让我觉得非常贴心。

此外，诊所使用的设备也很先进，整个治疗过程高效且安全。治疗结束后，医生还耐心地讲解了术后护理和注意事项，非常负责任。

总的来说，这次的就诊体验非常好，无论是服务态度还是专业水平，都让我感到放心。如果你也在寻找一家值得信赖的牙科诊所，我非常推荐这里！
reviews.textTranslated:
I recently had an implant over denture done at this dentist, and I was very satisfied with the whole process. First of all, the clinic environment is very clean, comfortable and relaxing. The reception staff were warm and courteous, attentive and explained every step in detail, which made people feel very reassured.

Dr Lim Sze Ming was very professional and patient. He examined the condition of my teeth in detail before treatment and formulated a suitable treatment plan for me. During the entire treatment process, the doctor worked carefully, tried to reduce my discomfort, and constantly asked me how I felt, which made me feel very considerate.

In addition, the equipment used in the clinic is also very advanced, making the entire treatment process efficient and safe. After the treatment, the doctor patiently explained the postoperative care and precautions, and was very responsible.

Overall, this medical experience was very good, both in terms of service attitude and professionalism, which made me feel at ease. If you are also looking for a trustworthy dental clinic, I highly recommend this place!

reviews.textTranslated: I am really not happy with the service at this clinic from the staff to the Doc. First of all, I wanted to get my teeth cleaned, which has changed over the years, I had to pay almost 5k because a male Doc (can't remember his name) did nerve treatment on my right tooth, which should have been fine. During the treatment, there was no screen for the patient to see. The staff fee for the treatment was 1k.. but the treatment made my tooth even more painful. The Doc advised me to go get a referral letter from the government clinic and take the letter to the dentist. What saddens me is that when I asked for a referral letter, what the Doc said to me, the Doc didn't give it to me unless I paid rm 30. Allahuakbar ... we are Muslims in the holy month of Ramadhan, this is still the case. While during my treatment, there was no screen for the Doc to see For me, the screen and explanation are very important for patients. I have already met with Doc Shafiqah to explain what happened and I did it well, I don't want to fight and drop their rice cooker. I forgot to first have Doc Shafiqah paste my tooth that came out. Doc Shafiqah didn't wash the remnants of my fillings that were years old and then filled and washed them in a relatively short time..rm 370 made many times my fillings come out and fester. As a result, I was very sick. I searched Google for a dental clinic that was open on Sundays..I also went to the UMMI clinic at Taman Koskam...I was amazed and comfortable with the service and treatment based on the instructions of Doc Salman and Doc Izah through the screen that allowed me to see for myself what had happened to my teeth. I had to do an x-ray for 5 minutes which was very painful and the fee was quite EXPENSIVE..I Relax, even though both my left and right teeth are still sore.. Imagine having to bite 1 last in the shape of a rather thick box inserted into my mouth and I have to bite to get a result of the image of the teeth from the roots.. Allahhuakbar 😭 shedding tears holding back the pain for the sake of getting the results of my teeth. After getting the results, the Doc had to remove the molar tooth that I use to bite food. Because in the past, every time I was pregnant, I had to remove the molar tooth. So my right front tooth no longer has any teeth to bite food. On my left front tooth, the place where Doc Shafiqah Palam had 3 places. Doc Salman and Doc Pakar worked hard to help save the tooth by cleaning and removing all the pieces of Doc Shafiqah Palam because there was a bacterial infection and pus. I had to break my fast, my pain, and thousands of dollars.. Estimated 4lbh, I'm going to sleep and work... Allahhuakbar... my treatment is not over yet. If I finish my treatment, I will get false teeth. I don't know if I will get dental implants or any other treatment to cover my innocent and sinful teeth, a creation of ALLAH SAW that is very valuable to his patients. I am happy but what I regret even though I have already met with Doc Shafiqah himself.. he told me to talk to that male Doc.. while the dental clinic is in the name of Doc Shafiqah..... strange. I have already referred to my brother-in-law Prof. Dr. Mustaffa Omar who is a PHT graduate in the United Kingdom... try Google and you will get it... my brother-in-law suggested that I sue. But my husband, if possible, does not want this case to continue. We, husband and wife, do not want it to happen to other patients like mine. Allah is the best and the most knowing in this holy month of Ramadhan.. prayers for those who are in the presence of Allah SAW accepted. Blessings are very important to find halal sustenance..the service of staff and patients needs to be taken care of. The money we get to feed our family will become our flesh and blood. "Let knowledge be a cubit.. Manners be a mountain.". Thank you.

reviews.name: Jagdeep Singh
reviews.text:
⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Highly Recommended!

I had an excellent experience with Dr. Abigail at Blessing Dental Care, Langkawi. She treated my chipped tooth with expert precision, ensuring a smooth and comfortable finish. I also had scaling and polishing done, and the entire process was handled professionally with great attention to detail.

What truly stood out was her patient-first approach, she recommended the best treatment option, which was actually the more affordable one, proving that she prioritizes patient care over profit. Her professionalism, skill, and honesty make her a rare find. I highly recommend Dr. Abigail to anyone looking for top-notch dental care in Langkawi

reviews.textTranslated: To be honest, the dentist was nice and talkative, but his skills were mediocre. Teeth cleaning was really painful (I had my teeth cleaned at other places, and it was definitely not that painful). I also had my teeth filled, and the area where the fillings were made every other day hurt for two weeks! I took Panadol every day to relieve pain, and it took about 2 weeks for the pain to subside. Just when I thought the matter was over, I didn’t expect that half of the teeth I had filled were cracked. It was less than three months old! I'm very angry now 😡😡

reviews.name: Jacqueline Teoh
reviews.text:
Union Dental
Dr Steve Tang Yee Chyuan

2021-09-25 开启了我的绑牙之路
2023-04-29 结束绑牙
在脱完牙套回去当天就已经发现牙缝有点大（绑牙其中一个好处是可以让牙齿不那么容易塞牙的，结果我是跟人家相反，我反而是吃东西牙缝会一直塞牙）
而且有一颗很深的蛀牙医生也没发现
所以在大约1-2个月内便复诊和告知医生牙缝和蛀牙的问题
医生：哎呀，这个应该在绑牙之前补掉的）🙄
当初医生给出的解决方案是
1）戴隐形牙套（必须自费）所以我拒绝了
2）把之前脱掉的牙套从新戴回去
，但因为婚礼很接近所以这个方案不可行
3）那就是用补牙的方式把缝补密，我接受了这个方案
由于我蛀牙的位置刚好是牙缝大的位置所以一起补了
我：靠补牙把牙缝补密不就需要一直补吗
医生：对，那你就找我补过（需自费）
但是从（09/12/2023 - 26/05/2025）补牙的地方掉了两次
没想过绑牙技术差，补牙技术也那么差
本来绑牙是为了让牙齿更美更好，结果绑了问题更多了。
在我绑牙还没结束之前，我也介绍我姐姐去了
我姐姐在一次复诊中
医生：还有什么问题吗
姐姐：没什么问题最重要不要有蛀牙就好，
医生再看了看
医生：哎呀，还真的有一颗蛀牙
姐姐：无语😓（所以是说我姐姐没提到的话就会跟我一样吗？）

*医生虽然每天都会见很多病人，但是每个人的牙齿就那么多，没了就没了，真的希望医生可以再细心一些，让我们病人付费的同时问题也可以解决
reviews.textTranslated:
Union Dental
Dr Steve Tang Yee Chyuan

2021-09-25 Started my journey of braces
2023-04-29 Finished braces
On the day after I took off my braces, I found that the gap between my teeth was a bit big (one of the benefits of braces is that it can make teeth less prone to food stuck in the teeth, but I am the opposite of others. I always get food stuck in my teeth when I eat)
And I have a deep cavity that the doctor didn’t find
So I went back for a follow-up visit in about 1-2 months and told the doctor about the gap and cavity
Doctor: Oh, this should be filled before braces)🙄
The solution given by the doctor at the time was
1) Wear invisible braces (must pay for it yourself) so I refused
2) Put the braces that I took off before back on
, but because the wedding was close, this solution was not feasible
3) That is to fill the gap with a filling, I accepted this solution
Since the location of my cavity happened to be the location of the large gap between my teeth, I filled it together
Me: If you fill the gap with a filling, don’t you need to keep filling it?
Doctor: Yes, then you can ask me to fill it (at your own expense)
But since (09/12/2023 - 26/05/2025) The fillings fell off twice
I never thought that the braces technique was so bad, and the filling technique was also so bad
The purpose of braces was to make the teeth more beautiful and better, but the braces caused more problems.
Before I finished the braces, I also introduced my sister to it
My sister was in a follow-up visit
The doctor: Do you have any other questions?
Sister: No problem, the most important thing is not to have cavities,
The doctor looked again
The doctor: Oh, there is really a cavity
Sister: Speechless😓 (So if my sister didn’t mention it, I would be the same?)

*Although the doctor sees many patients every day, everyone has so many teeth, and if they are gone, they are gone. I really hope that the doctor can be more careful so that we patients can solve the problem while paying.

reviews.text: Alhamdulillah, pengalaman utk 1st time yg cabut gigi, sgt baik.. ready for the next appointment 😊 Muka still kebas sebelah, bercakap pun mcm orang mabuk ubat 😂 But seriously, service kat Gov Dental Jubli memang 5 ⭐️! From the reception to the doctor, everyone is friendly, full of energy, and so positive.. I told you that it was my first time having a tooth extracted, the Dr and the team were very supportive, gently comforted me and calmly treated us who were panicking,, huhu, thank you so much Dr and team, tiptop service!! Amen yra🤲🏻

reviews.textTranslated: Myself is kind of afraid to pull teeth, paste teeth to all fear. Cracked teeth for almost 3 years let it be like that. Where can I brush my teeth? Finally, my face has swollen twice in the past 3 years. By taking care of a sick child, so surrender. A week before, I looked for a place, read all the reviews and asked my friends which places DO NOT PICK UP THE ANESTHETIC, AND DO NOT PAIN WHEN THE MOLAR TEETH IS EXTRACTED? CHEAP PASTHHHHH. Due to the last trauma of pulling out the upper molars 20 years ago, my brain is shaking. Alhamdulillah, a friend recommended Doctor Husli Dental Clinic at Lot 88, Ambangan Height, Sungai Petani Kedah. Myself is willing to come from Penang you know. Worth it. Friendly staff. The doctor is also friendly, likes to break his fast and is good at joking because maybe he can see that I have a fear of seeing a dentist. The numbing medicine disappears within 4 hours after tooth extraction. DIRECT ANESTHETIC INJECTION X FEELS LIKE A NEEDLE PICKING THE GUM, THE TEETH EXTRACT DOESN'T FEEL PAIN OR CONCUSSION AIH . Now, it's ready, huh.. The doctor is making fun of me, I'm a coward of this level. After this, I want to persuade my husband not to pull his teeth. 🤣Please help. 😶👍🏼💯

Keep up the good work, Dr Arzleen and team 😊❤👍

reviews.name: Muhammad Abdullah
reviews.text: just my advice after 3+ years braces, klu nak buat  detail and precise klinik ni tak mampu buat. bracket and wire installation not precise enough. tapi harga ok, staff ok, Dr. advice agak ego, kita fhm kemampuan klinik rmai org. walaupun kdg2 Dr. miss potong hujung wire, susun bracket tak tepat, lps pasang tak check balik. patient pulak kena advice Dr.. mintak betulkan wire tak nak. dah sah2 pasang silap cross wire tu. ttba nak end service buang braces, sbb apa sbb payment dah lebih target? nak buka sgt braces, tgok2  mggu ni, my teeth gigi taring sblah bwh clash dgn atas bila gigit sbb wire n bracket pasang tak kemas n plug filler pulak tak remove awal2. dtg bulan2 tukar getah je, bracket tak check pon kedudukan betul ke tidak. dah ckp dah cross wire tu. end up kena buat klinik lain la..service klu cincai mmg out..  takkan nak psg braces balik 2x keja.
reviews.textTranslated: just my advice after 3+ years of braces, if you want to do detail and precision this clinic can't do it. bracket and wire installation is not precise enough. but the price is ok, staff is ok, Dr. advice is a bit egoistic, we understand the capabilities of many clinics. although sometimes Dr. misses cutting the end of the wire, arranging the bracket incorrectly, then installing it without checking back. the patient needs Dr.'s advice. ask to fix the wire, but don't want it. It's already installed the wrong cross wire. I don't want to end the service to remove the braces, why is the payment already over the target? I really want to open the braces, look at this week, my canine teeth are already clashing with the top when I bite because the wire and bracket were installed incorrectly and the plug filler was not removed early. After a few months, they just changed the rubber, the bracket didn't even check if the position was correct. The cross wire has already been checked. I end up having to go to another clinic.. the service if you mess up is really out.. I don't want to put braces back on twice.

Most probably will request him for my second wisdom tooth extraction. Cuma dari segi interior klinik tu lawa rupanya bila tengok gambar kat google review. Maybe klinik nak jimat letrik. reviews.textTranslated: Just had my minor operation with Dr Zul. Highly recommended to get the treatment here. The surgery on the youngest tooth was already scary, but thank God everything went smoothly under his treatment. There is no pain even during the injection. Sergeant gentle. The consultation was easy to understand and very informative. The assistant staff is also very friendly. Help pt to calm down during the procedure. A+ for all. Ohh there is a kids corner too. Reasonable price. Most probably will request him for my second wisdom tooth extraction. Only in terms of the interior of the clinic, it looks bad when you look at the pictures on google review. Maybe the clinic wants to save electricity. The lights don't even turn on at all. No waiting area. Then go to the toilet without turning on the light. It's gloomy.

reviews.responseFromOwnerText:
Assalamualaikum, kita telah cuba hubungi Cik untuk mendengar sendiri apa kekurangan dari pihak klinik dan masalah yang Cik hadapi, namun tiada respond dari pihak Cik. Untuk makluman Cik, sebelum suntikan dilakukan kali kedua sebentar tadi, Cik telah dimaklumkan dan diberitahu bahawa ianya akan sedikit terasa sakit disebabkan kita melakukan suntikan ubat kebas di celahan ligament gigi (Intraligament Injection), Cik juga telah faham dan cabutan pun turut berjaya dilakukan. Ubatan terutama antibiotik tidak diberikan disebabkan Cik tidak mempunyai bengkak atau tanda jangkitan yang jelas mahupun rasa sakit yang kuat, namun hanya masalah gusi surut dan gigi terangkat senget yang tidak memerlukan ubat. Rawatan yang sepatutnya juga telah dilakukan, namun begitu harap maaf sebarang kekurangan dan kelemahan dari pihak klinik. 
Sekian, terima kasih dan semoga cepat sembuh 🤲.

reviews.name: NUR AZYYATI BINTI ABDUL RAHIM STUDENT
reviews.text:
I’ve been to this clinic a few times and generally had no major issues. However, during my last visit, I did a filling for two teeth and was charged RM500, which I found quite pricey.

What’s more frustrating is that just 1.5 months later, one of the fillings came off. I called the clinic to ask if I could come back to get it fixed for free, since it hadn’t even been two months — but they said I’d have to pay the full price again. 🤯

After already paying so much, I expected at least some tolerance or understanding. Unfortunately, they told me the warranty is only one month. 🥲

Disappointed with the lack of flexibility and follow-up care, especially given the high charges.
reviews.responseFromOwnerText:
Hi NUR AZYYATI , 
First and foremost, we sincerely apologize for any disappointment or inconvenience you may have experienced.

Upon reviewing our records, we would like to clarify that the fillings were completed on 24th February, which is nearly four months ago, not 1.5 months as mentioned.

Additionally, our clinical notes indicate that a total of four fillings were done on multiple surfaces of different teeth during your visit, not just on two teeth.

We always strive to maintain high standards in both treatment quality and pricing. However, based on your feedback and our records, there seems to be a discrepancy. It's important to note that filling dislodgement can occur, especially in cases where the tooth structure is already compromised.

We would encourage you to return for a consultation with our doctor, who will be able to assess the situation and advise whether a replacement or further treatment is needed.

Thank you for your understanding, and we look forward to assisting you further.

ownerUpdates.text:
“Baru rasa bebas bila tak perlu buka-pasang gigi palsu dah 😭”

Sebelum ni, patient ni pakai gigi palsu jenis buka-pasang (removable). Tapi lepas buat rawatan Fibre Reinforced Composite Bridge (FRC), terus rasa legaaa sebab…

✔️ Tak perlu buka-pasang
✔️ Rasa lebih natural & selesa
✔️ Makan pun confident balik

Dia siap cakap, “Menyesal tak buat awal dari dulu. Senang sangat, duduk je terus siap. Tak payah buka-pakai dah”

Kalau ada gigi depan kosong, especially sebab patah atau gigi lama tercabut — FRC ni antara pilihan paling cepat & cantik untuk tampung ruang tu ✨

Rawatan ni biasanya siap dalam 1 kali datang je.

📩 DM kami untuk consult dengan Doktor dulu 😁

🔺 Dulu senyum mesti cover mulut...
Rasa tak konfiden bila gigi jarang-jarang.

Tapi semua berubah lepas buat rawatan Veneer composite.

Sekarang?
Senyum lebar, gambar pun tak sabar nak ambil ✨

Rawatan yang cepat & hasil natural.
Macam gigi sendiri, tapi lagi cantik!

Jom DM kami untuk set temujanji👍🏼
Haa, siapa kat sini dah pakai braces? Jangan lupa cara penjagaan braces 🤗☺️

🔺 Hai semua, mari kami share prosedur sebelum memakai braces 😄✌🏻 

Nak gigi cantik tersusun, jom DM kami sekarang untuk temujanji 👍🏼

“Dulu patah… sekarang kembali segak 💪🏼”

Sebelum ni, malu nak senyum sebab gigi depan patah. Tapi dengan veneer, kita tak cuma betulkan rupa — kita pulihkan keyakinan.

✅ Gigi depan nampak sama panjang
✅ Warna sekata & bersih
✅ Tak perlu risau senyum senget dah 😁

Kadang kita fikir patah tu permanent. Tapi sebenarnya masih boleh dibaiki — dengan cara yang cepat, selamat & tahan lama ✨

Kalau anda pun ada masalah yang sama, jom DM kami untuk set temujanji👍🏼

🔺 Di Klinik Pergigian Akasia, kami jaga kesihatan gigi anda & keluarga dengan teliti. Dari rawatan asas hingga cosmetic dentistry, kami sedia membantu!

✅ Doktor berpengalaman
✅ Peralatan moden
✅ Rawatan untuk semua peringkat umur
✅ Suasana selesa dan mesra

Tempah temujanji anda sekarang! ⏰

🔺 Gigi atau tampalan pecah? Tampalan warna tak sekata? Jangan risau, boleh cun balik!

Puan ni datang sebab tampalan gigi depan dia pecah dan bentuk tak sekata. Sebagai cikgu, mestilah nak senyum yakin depan student kan?

Kita buat Composite Veneer — cepat, tak sakit & terus nampak beza!
Tengok je lah before & after, macam magic!

Kalau anda pun ada masalah gigi pecah, renggang atau tak rata, jom DM kami. Kita bantu bagi senyuman baru yang wow!
🔺 Periksa gigi anda 6 bulan sekali, atau sekurang kurangnya setahun sekali agar dapat mencegah sebarang penyakit pergigian dari bertambah teruk dan menjaga kesihatan mulut anda ✅🦷

🔺 Gigi cantik berseri selepas dipasang bridge ni😍

Dental bridge adalah gigi palsu jenis kekal, cantik seperti gigi asli dan tak perlu ditanggalkan✨ 

Anda ada gigi yang hilang? Jom buat bridge/ jambatan gigi 👍🏼

⚠️ Gigi kuning mengganggu keyakinan diri anda? 😔 

Kami memahami perasaan anda dan kami sedia membantu. 🙌🏽 Rawatan pemutihan gigi kami boleh mengubah senyuman anda. 😁 

Bayangkan betapa yakinnya anda dengan gigi yang lebih putih! 🌟 

Jom buat temu janji hari ini. ☎️

reviews.name: Kumarendren A.S.
reviews.text:
First and foremost, I would like to extend my deepest gratitude to the entire team at this clinic.

This marks my third visit, and I must sincerely say that each experience has surpassed expectations, largely due to the exceptional hospitality demonstrated by the staff. A special acknowledgment goes to Dr. Anwar, whose kindness and attentiveness made the treatment feel truly personalized and exclusive.

Despite working far away on the east coast, and having experienced intermittent toothache over the past two weeks, I chose to delay seeking care until my planned trip to my hometown in Jitra, solely to consult Dr. Anwar. My wife had advised me to visit a nearby dentist, but I insisted on waiting, confident in the quality of care I would receive here. Thankfully, the discomfort remained manageable.

As anticipated, Dr. Anwar’s gentle and meticulous approach to both assessment and treatment was commendable. He even took the time to retrieve my previous dental records and inquire about my progress—an act that reflects his dedication and professionalism.

It is rare to come across a healthcare professional, especially in dentistry, who embodies such genuine care and excellence, more so within one’s own hometown.

I look forward to future visits. Keep up the outstanding work, team!

My dentist explained my procedure in great detail and made me feel very comfortable. Modern equipment, very clean, inviting and all staff I met were kind and polite. My language is English and there was no language barrier.

reviews.name: AISYA NORMI BINTI MUHAMMAD YUZIR (JPN-PERAK)
reviews.text: Had a sudden toothache last night and found this dental clinic through Google. Called them this morning and managed to get a 10am appointment. The young male doctor was friendly and explained everything clearly. The staff were also kind and helpful. Modern equipment and great service overall. Very satisfied!

reviews.name: Mercator Sands
reviews.text: I have had dental work done in many countries in Europe and the America's. I have had some good experiences but nothing as smooth as Dr. Boey. They have the latest technology including 3D imaging for making crowns, and MRI. Dr. He takes pictures during the procedure (I had a triple root canal) and applies the Novocain in stages, unlike a few clinics I have been to, giving it time to act so you feel nothing. I have had dozens of teeth worked on. This was the best numbing technique I have ever encountered. I was really worried I was going to feel some pain. There was none. Nothing. Incredible. It's such a pleasure to be guided down a path to a well executed procedure by someone that really knows what he is doing. He explained what he was doing and why, I felt totally safe. I would fly from anywhere in the world to get this quality of work.

reviews.name: Siti Faridah
reviews.text:
Kali ke 3 saya ke sini..pertama kali saya sangat berpuas hati..dapat Dr perempuan..sgat cermat cabut garham Harini,esok dah lega..ubat tahan sakit Hany 2 biji saya makan..kali ke 2 bawa anak,dapat Dr perempuan jugak..anak kata Dr tu cabut xsakit pun..ubat tahan sakit 2 biji jugak makan dan terus lega..kali ke3 saya datang nk cabut garham satu lg..dapat Dr lelaki..saya xselesa dgan Dr tu..cara dia kasar..cucuk ubat kebas pun pahit..sebelum ni sy dan ank dapat perisa strawberi..kali ni dapat yg pahit..lepas tu habis luka bibir
dan gusi saya..cabut hari jumaat,hari Ahad masih xlega..ubat tahan sakit dh 5 biji saya makan..masih sakit..nk MKN pun susah..bibir dan gusi luka..kenapa masa sy cabut dekat Dr perempuan xda luka pun..saya xtahu ada Dr lelaki kat situ..lepas ni kalau nk buat rawatan gigi sy nak tanya dulu..kalau boleh nak Dr perempuan..maaf cakap..
reviews.textTranslated: This is my 3rd time here..first time I was very satisfied..got a female doctor..very careful to remove the wart. Today, tomorrow I will be relieved..I only took 2 painkillers..2nd time I brought my son, got a female doctor too..son said the doctor pulled it out without any pain..took 2 painkillers and immediately felt relieved..3rd time I came to get another wart removed..got a male doctor..I was uncomfortable with the doctor..his way was rough..the numbing medicine was also bitter..before this me and my son got strawberry flavor..this time got bitter..after that my lip and gum were gone..got it out on Friday, still not relieved on Sunday..I have taken 5 painkillers..still hurts..even if I have to do MKN..lips and gums hurt..why when I got it removed by a female doctor there was no pain..I didn't know there was a male doctor there..after that If I want to get dental treatment, I want to ask first..if I can get a female doctor..sorry to say..
reviews.responseFromOwnerText: Salam puan maaf atas kesulitan. Puan boleh datang semula jika sakit tidak berkurangan ya.

reviews.name: hazwan Faiz
reviews.text: P cabut gigi Klinik lain (klinik tu Dr dan Staf OK). Cuma, bila balik, berlaku bleeding non stop smpai mlm. Call clinic tu, xdpt sbb dh ttup. Pastu Call klinik al-Fateh. kbetulan  waktu tu ada Dr Pakar. So trus ke sana.. Dr bjaya stopkan bleeding. Tq kpd semua staff terutama Dr Najwa..
reviews.textTranslated: I had my tooth extracted at another clinic (the clinic's Dr and staff were OK). However, when I returned, I was bleeding non-stop until nightfall. I called the clinic, but it was closed because it was closed. So I called the al-Fateh clinic. It happened that there was a specialist Dr at that time. So I went there. Dr. Bjaya stopped the bleeding. Thank you to all the staff, especially Dr. Najwa.

reviews.name: Juwairiah Jamil
reviews.text: Baru selesai betul-betul empat rawatan di klinik ini, melibatkan 17 kali kunjungan, dan beberapa review. Saya yakin untuk meneruskan sekaligus satu-satu rawatan sehingga selesai kerana ketelitian doktor yang merawat. Selain itu, doktor ‘menyelesaikan’ kerja-kerja yang tidak selesai oleh doktor sebelumnya yang merawat saya di klinik lain, hampir 10 tahun lalu. Apa yang tak puas hati di hati saya, seolah-oleh difahami oleh doktor. Beliau akan melakukan kerja-kerja rawatan gigi sesuai dengan keinginan dan cita rasa saya. Sebarang masalah boleh dirunding untuk diberi rawatan susulan segera. Semua rawatan yang diberikan adalah secara lemah lembut dan tidak kasar, juga tidak menakutkan. Baru nak berangan ada doktor gigi yang serasi dalam tempoh masa yang panjang, tapi setakat ini sahaja nampaknya. Mujur doktor sempat merawat saya untuk setiap jenis rawatan yang agak kritikal itu, kerana saya sejenis sukar ke klinik gigi, dan sukar mempercayai doktor gigi.😂 Apapun rezeki doktor di tempat lain. Selamat maju jaya. ☺️
reviews.textTranslated: Just finished four treatments at this clinic, involving 17 visits, and several reviews. I am confident to continue with each treatment until it is finished because of the thoroughness of the doctor who treated me. In addition, the doctor 'completed' the work that was not completed by the previous doctor who treated me at another clinic, almost 10 years ago. What was not satisfied in my heart, it seemed to be understood by the doctor. He will do the dental treatment work according to my wishes and tastes. Any problems can be negotiated for immediate follow-up treatment. All the treatments given are gentle and not rough, nor are they scary. I just wanted to dream of having a dentist who is compatible for a long period of time, but it seems that's all. Fortunately, the doctor was able to treat me for every type of treatment that was quite critical, because I have a hard time going to the dental clinic, and it's hard to trust dentists. 😂 Whatever the fortune of the doctor elsewhere. Good luck. ☺️

If you're in or near Kulim, this clinic is definitely worth a visit. Will be coming again for future treatments!

reviews.text: First time pergi dentist yg selesa, rate b40 & mesra kanak-kanak. sy buat 3 tampalan gigi disini. doktor beri penjelasan jelas. gigi yg ditampal pun selesa & tiada lagi denyut sakit. recommended korg yg sakit gigi boleh datang sni area alor setar 🥰

reviews.text: very recommended! easy to deal..the doctor was  friendly and professional about explaining my dental problem

reviews.name: Amuta Varaszi
reviews.text: Very good doctor n friendly staff....price also reasonable.....thank you Dr.komathy n staff

reviews.name: Khairun Nisa
reviews.text: Saya buat minor oral surgery (gigi bongsu). Alhamdulillah semua okay. Sepanjang proses takda rasa sakit sbb Dr bagi bius. Sebelum & selepas operation Dr Khoo Susan bagi penjelasan yg jelas. Semasa proses semua okay. Staff buka cerita Mr Bean dkt TV. Haha 😂 jadi saya tkda la rasa nervous. Terima kasih Dr & staff. 😊
reviews.textTranslated: I had minor oral surgery (wisdom teeth). Thank God everything was okay. There was no pain during the process because the Dr. gave anesthesia. Before & after the operation, Dr. Khoo Susan gave a clear explanation. During the process, everything was okay. The staff played the Mr. Bean story on TV. Haha 😂 so I didn't feel nervous. Thank you Dr. & staff. 😊
